data.title: Pancham (TV Series)
data.text: Pancham is an Indian TV series aired on Zee TV channel, based on the life of a young teenage boy, Harpaul Rana, who wants to set the 'world' right without 'preaching'. The series premiered on August 30, 2004, and aired every Monday - Thursday at 1pm IST. Rani Life. Pancham is currently being repeated on Zee TV Usa on Monday-Thursday at 6:00 pm!
